 * group:texts => 评价内容
 * texts.testimonial_1_name => 评价1姓名:text:Rajesh Kumar (Mumbai)
 * texts.testimonial_1_rating => 评价1评分:text:⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
 * texts.testimonial_1_content => 评价1内容:textarea:Best Teen Patti app I've used! I've been playing for 6 months and won ₹45,000 so far.
 * texts.testimonial_2_name => 评价2姓名:text:Priya Sharma (Delhi)
 * texts.testimonial_2_rating => 评价2评分:text:⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
 * texts.testimonial_2_content => 评价2内容:textarea:Fair game, genuine payments. After winning ₹8,000 in my first month, I'm hooked!
 * texts.testimonial_3_name => 评价3姓名:text:Amit Patel (Ahmedabad)
 * texts.testimonial_3_rating => 评价3评分:text:⭐⭐⭐⭐☆
 * texts.testimonial_3_content => 评价3内容:textarea:Love the game variety. Won ₹12K last week in a tournament.
